@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@model GrcMvc.Controllers.TenantLoginViewModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Auth_TenantLoginV2Title"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
    var version = ViewData["Version"] as string;
    var tenantSlug = ViewData["TenantSlug"] as string;
}

<div class="auth-form">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header text-center bg-primary text-white">
            <h4><i class="bi bi-building"></i> @L["Auth_TenantLoginEnhanced"]</h4>
            @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(version))
            {
                <small class="badge bg-light text-dark">@version</small>
            }
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="alert alert-info">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                <strong>@L["Auth_SessionBasedTenantClaims"]</strong>
            </div>
            
            @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(tenantSlug))
            {
                <div class="alert alert-success">
                    <strong>@L["Auth_Tenant"]</strong> @tenantSlug
                </div>
            }
            
            <form asp-action="TenantLogin" asp-controller="AccountV2" method="post">
                @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                <div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"></div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Email" class="form-label">@L["Auth_EmailLabel"]</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-text"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></span>
                        <input asp-for="Email" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Auth_EmailPlaceholder"]" autofocus required />
                    </div>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Email" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Password" class="form-label">@L["Auth_PasswordLabel"]</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-text"><i class="bi bi-lock"></i></span>
                        <input asp-for="Password" class="form-control" type="password" placeholder="@L["Auth_PasswordPlaceholder"]" required />
                    </div>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Password" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="TenantId" class="form-label">@L["Auth_TenantIdFieldLabel"]</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-text"><i class="bi bi-building"></i></span>
                        <input asp-for="TenantId" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Auth_TenantIdPlaceholder"]" required />
                    </div>
                    <span asp-validation-for="TenantId" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="TenantSlug" class="form-label">@L["Auth_TenantSlugLabel"]</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-text"><i class="bi bi-tag"></i></span>
                        <input asp-for="TenantSlug" class="form-control" placeholder="@L["Auth_TenantSlugPlaceholder"]" value="@tenantSlug" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label asp-for="Role" class="form-label">@L["Auth_RoleLabel"]</label>
                    <select asp-for="Role" class="form-select">
                        <option value="">@L["Auth_SelectRole"]</option>
                        <option value="TenantAdmin">Tenant Admin</option>
                        <option value="TenantUser">Tenant User</option>
                        <option value="ComplianceOfficer">Compliance Officer</option>
                        <option value="RiskManager">Risk Manager</option>
                        <option value="Auditor">Auditor</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <input type="hidden" asp-for="ReturnUrl" value="@ViewData["ReturnUrl"]" />

                <div class="mb-3 form-check">
                    <input asp-for="RememberMe" class="form-check-input" />
                    <label asp-for="RememberMe" class="form-check-label">@L["Auth_RememberMeLabel"]</label>
                </div>

                <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> @L["Auth_LoginToTenantEnhanced"]
                    </button>
                </div>

                <hr />

                <div class="text-center">
                    <p>
                        <a asp-action="Login" asp-controller="AccountV2">@L["Auth_RegularLogin"]</a> |
                        <a asp-action="ForgotPassword" asp-controller="Account">@L["Auth_ForgotPassword"]</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </form>
            
            <div class="mt-3">
                <h6>@L["Auth_V2SessionBasedClaims"]</h6>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> @L["Auth_TenantContextInSession"]</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> @L["Auth_FixesClaimsBug"]</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> @L["Auth_FasterTenantSwitching"]</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> @L["Auth_NoDatabaseOverhead"]</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/account/tenant-login" class="btn btn-sm btn-link">@L["Auth_SwitchToLegacyTenantLogin"]</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @{await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");}
}
